images.alt:
An array of folded pieces of fabric.
Across the top are a two-tone blue design of portraits of girls and mermaids framed in wreaths and surrounded by plant motifs;
2 different shades of blue (royal and light turquoise) with sailboat and lighthouse motifs in white;
Little green spade-shaped leaves on a pale blue background; and
A deep kelly green with splotches of darker colour.
And along the bottom:
Bright kites on pale blue;
Rows of multicoloured animals holding hands on medium green; and
Turtles of many colours, whose shells are little houses with doors and windows, like trailers, on white, with little flowers.

